      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">The good news? You have options. Real options that don't involve draining your retirement or maxing out credit cards at 24% interest.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mt-10 mb-4">Are There Roofing Contractors That Offer Financing for Storm Damage?</h2>
