      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6"><strong>Insurance + Financing Combo:</strong> If you have storm damage, insurance may cover part of your roof. Financing can cover your deductible and any upgrades insurance won't pay for.</p>

      <div class="bg-primary/10 border-l-4 border-primary p-6 my-8 rounded-r-lg">
