        <p class="text-gray-700">"I've seen families put off roof repairs for years because they thought they couldn't afford it. Then a small leak becomes a major mold problem, and suddenly they're looking at a $30,000 bill instead of a $12,000 one. The monthly payment on financing is almost always cheaper than waiting."</p>
