      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">At Gimo's Roofing, we partner with EnerBank USA to offer financing options that make sense for real families. Here's the step-by-step:</p>

      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-600 space-y-4">
