        <li><strong>Choose Your Terms:</strong> Pick a monthly payment that works for your budget. We offer terms from 12 months to 144 months.</li>
        <li><strong>We Start Work:</strong> Once approved, we schedule your project. You don't pay anything until the work is complete and you're satisfied.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mt-10 mb-4">What Does a New Roof Actually Cost Per Month?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Let's look at real numbers for a typical Jacksonville home:</p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Example: $15,000 Roof Replacement</p>
