      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-secondary mt-6 mb-2">What roofing companies offer financing near me?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">In Jacksonville, several reputable companies offer financing, including Gimo's Roofing. When researching <strong>what roofing companies offer financing</strong>, look for those who partner with established lenders rather than offering "in-house" financing with unclear terms.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-secondary mt-6 mb-2">Will applying hurt my credit score?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">The initial application is usually a soft pull that doesn't affect your score. A hard pull only happens if you accept the loan and move forward.</p>

